{"tid":918412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80大壽殺豬慶生 壽星遭肥豬踢進滾水致6成皮膚燙傷","createTime":"2018-11-27T07:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T05:52:28.000Z","uid":75969,"like":754,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"f4f51591f94c23f41832b27f57d8b6cfb8c8fce7","tid":918412,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181127/_2018112715425659128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181127%2F_2018112715425659128.jpg&h=c0b56bed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n湖北省鳳山鎮村民楊河柳日前80歲大壽，<span style=\"color: red;\">他請人殺豬慶賀，卻被瀕死的豬踢入滾水鍋中致嚴重燙傷。</span>現今面對30萬元人民幣高昂醫療費，其家人目前已花費逾五萬元，楊家正面臨沉重負擔。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，楊河柳11月19日慶祝80歲壽辰，當日中午與親友吃過壽宴後，請村內有名的屠夫把自己養的一隻100多公斤的豬殺掉。屠夫稱村內殺豬一般會先燒一鍋滾水，待豬隻被宰殺後在豬腳割開口，然後用打氣筒充氣，最後將豬隻用滾水燙一下方便剃豬毛。事發時肥豬垂死掙扎，亂腳將楊踢進滾水鍋中，眾人立即將他撈起。<br />\n<br />\n楊隨即被送到羅田縣人民醫院，醫生因其傷勢太重建議轉送到武漢專業治療燙傷的醫院。武漢醫院醫生檢查後，稱楊60%面積被燙傷，而背部、肩部更達三級燙傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/874468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F874468&d=LFry4mU5MBWBgVoBxpk3xfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0e56f987\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F874468&h=e488fcfa\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/874468</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d858f2c1f2a5abe3aa4a168e349e3747f15b0ff","tid":918412,"uid":127032,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040a59274850645258c520e29fbe42abc688fbc4","tid":918412,